{"tid":474131,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿仙奴官方Twitter玩得太過火？","createTime":"2017-11-20T01:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T09:32:23.000Z","uid":333,"like":54,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ad5cafde458e582d9a8fb7e7d26b5e8527613edb","tid":474131,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:14:24.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Q%2FzATyi%2BLt4M8DTUOBGFiS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5b33e9e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴官方Twitter回應了一位記者在社交網開的玩笑，怎料引發了一起「網絡欺凌」。<br />\n<br />\n事情源自周六打吡前，阿仙奴在社交網Twitter上展開了一個「打吡戰最佳11人選」的投票，號召球迷發表自己心中意見。《每日郵報》體育記者葛夫頓（Adam Crafton）響應是次活動，但滿帶諷刺地選了一隊只有熱刺球員的陣容。最終阿仙奴2球擊敗了北倫敦的死敵，而阿仙奴官方Twitter亦意氣風發的在葛夫頓的貼文上回應了一段「奧斯爾嘆茶」的幽默短片回敬。<br />\n<br />\n只是作為英超知名球會，阿仙奴坐擁1230萬Twitter粉絲，這個回應儼然將葛夫頓推向數以千計阿仙奴球迷的手上。最終不少球迷都在葛夫頓的Twitter上發放負能量，令他忍受不了：「恭喜阿仙奴勝出，只是她們的回應會讓1230萬球迷看到，令我一直受到別人的滋擾，包括反猶太人言論、濫用同性戀言論與及希望我死的言論。我暫時還處理得到，但我真的建議球會不要重施故技了。」<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴官方亦很識相，站在葛夫頓的一方回應：「我們沒有任何冒犯葛夫頓的意圖，對於他的遭遇我們感到失望，並向滋擾者提出強烈譴責。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : Twitter圖片"},{"pid":"204258a6c13f297329ac841c83f60df758a22a83","tid":474131,"uid":2169,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:16:58.000Z","msg":"抵撚死啦"},{"pid":"3a86943fe501ddaf4db6c2661a94adb082239a71","tid":474131,"uid":4496,"like":98,"dislike":2,"score":96,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:17:48.000Z","msg":"個記者自己挑熱狗機先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n輸打贏要"},{"pid":"930c089968c30191c4119ce42001a745862dd7b0","tid":474131,"uid":27866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:18:09.000Z","msg":"🤣"},{"pid":"6f3a10f25707a199f2a4fa90fe627e97f9d28d56","tid":474131,"uid":38189,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:21:34.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"5fb5f05dcae1cb59d9cafebfaf385509e62da72f","tid":474131,"uid":50740,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:28:03.000Z","msg":"贏你3分要受氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9ed4e4de2ab7014aa3daf0f7dd39f4abd99214","tid":474131,"uid":14965,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:28:29.000Z","msg":"雲膠條廢佬又搞小動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb299adce839414bdb3e235b1e9bc65c35fe6143","tid":474131,"uid":97080,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:30:05.000Z","msg":"熱狗真係麻撚煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28cf480a0859265338167f7de9ca8d1ae7776a0e","tid":474131,"uid":34468,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T01:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.cool-gif.com/media/gif/28/88/288852a8e806a58e6e8fca692ef079bb/cool.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool-gif.com%2Fmedia%2Fgif%2F28%2F88%2F288852a8e806a58e6e8fca692ef079bb%2Fcool.gif&h=f080bbd9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ba456deb39d18e4c773eafdba982a2ab44c87c6","tid":474131,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:10:05.000Z","msg":"先撩者賤"},{"pid":"fe116b493de13f9232db58ee7961a4929358f388","tid":474131,"uid":32938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:22:59.000Z","msg":"玩唔起唔好學人串啦"},{"pid":"0465eca97e8fff6d7315e0b2fc3a77a0558a2bac","tid":474131,"uid":51453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:24:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://www.cool-gif.com/media/gif/28/88/288852a8e806a58e6e8fca692ef079bb/cool.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool-gif.com%2Fmedia%2Fgif%2F28%2F88%2F288852a8e806a58e6e8fca692ef079bb%2Fcool.gif&h=f080bbd9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\ndiu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468a7d6423f35de791c806e4e049978702edb446","tid":474131,"uid":187,"